Package: eebpf
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libbpf1, libelf1t64 | libelf1, zlib1g, python3-openai
Maintainer: Li Yan <15008695828@163.com>
Description: eBPF-based system anomaly observation and root cause analysis tool
 eebpf is a lightweight system observability tool based on eBPF (libbpf + CO-RE).
 It covers 5 anomaly scenarios: CPU, I/O, memory, lock contention, and syscall hotspots.
 Outputs structured Markdown diagnosis reports and JSON data.
 Requires Linux kernel 6.6+ with CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_BTF.
